front.title: •Commander Brandei
front.gametext: Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Once during each of your control phases, when aboard a Star Destroyer or at any docking bay, may use 1 Force to take one TIE into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.
front.lore: Technical Services Officer of the Fleet Support Branch. Responsible for keeping Executor's 12 TIE squadrons serviced and combat ready. Just received transfer to Judicator.

pulls: One TIE when at a Star Destroyer or any docking bay
combo: Commander Brandei + Sienar Fleet Systems + Dreaded Imperial Starfleet + TIE's with matching pilots.
